Six things to know

Stick the objectives
The exam sticks to the objectives closely, so get them down

Know the documentation
You are able to use the documentation, so know where everything is located. Get familiar with it, and know where to look.

Use oc --help and oc adm --help
The oc --help, oc <command> --help, oc adm --help, and oc adm <command> --help commands are you friends

Time
Three hours may seem like a lot of time, but its goes by fast. Really focus on the first three tips on this link --they will help you with your time management.

Read carefolly
Though there are many ways to complete most tasks, how they want things named and set up is very precise.

Any Answer is better than no answer
Dont leave anything blank. Partial credit is better than no credit.